title: 10/29/20 HOUR 3- Johnny Bench
itunes:title: 10/29/20 HOUR 3- Johnny Bench
description:
Johnny Bench tells Dan which merchandise from his playing career is going up for auction. Johnny says that most of his memorabilia is in boxes anyways, but does say that his Golden Glove from the year he was an All-Star could go for about 50k.
